last_episode_to_air.name: Grand Finale
last_episode_to_air.overview: It's the finale! The queens return for an electrifying reunion and the finalists tackle the ultimate Lip-Sync Smackdown. Who will RuPaul crown Queen of the Mothertucking World?

name: RuPaul's Drag Race UK vs The World
original_name: RuPaul's Drag Race UK vs The World
overview: RuPaul host as nine international queens compete to be Queen of the Mothertucking World.

seasons.name: Series 1
seasons.overview: The UK is the host nation as nine fan favorite queens enter the international arena to compete for the title of "Queen of the Mothertucking World!”. Each week their charisma, uniqueness, nerve, and talent is put to the test through next level fashion, dancing, singing, and comedy.

seasons.name: Series 2
seasons.overview: We're headed back to the Top of the Mothertucking World! RuPaul's Drag Race UK vs The World is back, starring queens from across the Drag Race franchise competing to be crowned Queen of the Mothertucking World.

episodes.name: Global Glamazons
episodes.overview: In this opening episode, head judge RuPaul introduces the global glamazons to each other for the first time and sets them their first challenge - to stage their very own royal command performance. With their future in the competition already on the line, each queen is keen to impress as they perform in a talent show fit for a queen.

episodes.name: RuPaul Ball
episodes.overview: The fierce international Drag Race competition continues, and this week it’s the RuPaul Ball! In a celebration of all things RuPaul, the queens must serve three looks on the runway, including an outfit they must create from scratch that Mama Ru herself would want to wear.

episodes.name: West End Wendys
episodes.overview: The fierce international competition to be crowned Queen of the Mothertucking World continues.Seven global glamazons remain, and this week the pressure amplifies, as their stage presence and their singing and dancing skills are seriously tested in a celebration of musical theatre. The queens are performing West End Wendys - The Rusical.

episodes.name: Snatch Game
episodes.overview: The fierce international competition to be crowned Queen of the Mothertucking World continues, and this week it’s the legendary Drag Race challenge: the Snatch Game... but with a twist! With iconic team captains Katie Price and Michelle Visage at the helm, the queens showcase their best celebrity impressions and improv skills in an attempt to make Mama Ru laugh.

episodes.name: Semifinals
episodes.overview: The fierce international competition to crown the Queen of the Mothertucking World reaches the nail-biting semi-finals! This week, the queens are tasked with an all-singing, all-dancing challenge: performing their own version of one of RuPaul’s classic hits. Little Mix star Jade Thirlwall coaches the queens as they record their vocals before joining RuPaul, Michelle Visage and Graham Norton on the judging panel as the fate of yet another queen is decided

episodes.name: Grand Finale
episodes.overview: It’s the Grand Finale! The UK hosted as nine legendary Drag Race queens from around the world entered the workroom to compete for the title of Queen of the Mothertucking World. Now, six weeks later, RuPaul is about to crown his winner. Which queen will be elevated to true legendary status and do their country proud?

1.name: Series 1
1.overview: The UK is the host nation as nine fan favorite queens enter the international arena to compete for the title of "Queen of the Mothertucking World!”. Each week their charisma, uniqueness, nerve, and talent is put to the test through next level fashion, dancing, singing, and comedy.

episodes.name: The Queens' Variety Show
episodes.overview: The famous race steps up to Olympian level as elite Drag Race queens from around the world take on the UK in a bid to be Mama Ru's favourite. Richard E. Grant joins in the fun.

episodes.name: The Happy Ending Ball
episodes.overview: The Olympics of drag continues as supermodel Adwoa Aboah joins RuPaul as guest judge, and the queens race against the clock to create a fairy-tale outfit suitable for a princess.

episodes.name: Drag Race World
episodes.overview: The queens attempt to make Mama Ru laugh as they create adverts for their own Drag Race-themed immersive experiences. Grammy-winning pop star Kim Petras joins the judging panel.

episodes.name: Snatch Game
episodes.overview: Jane McDonald and Sinitta join the queens as they tackle the iconic Snatch Game challenge whilst Olympic gold medallist and longtime Drag Race stan Tom Daley guest judges.

episodes.name: Seven!: The Rusical
episodes.overview: The competition and drama ramp up as the queens are tasked with staging Drag Race’s most challenging Rusical yet, and singer-songwriter Self Esteem joins RuPaul as guest judge.

episodes.name: Strictly Come Prancing
episodes.overview: Strictly legends Motsi Mabuse, Janette Manrara and Aljaž Škorjanec guest star as the queens take on a high level, high stakes dance-off with a twist in Strictly Come Prancing.

episodes.name: The Haters Wedding Roast
episodes.overview: It's the semi-finals! And The queens’ stand-up skills are tested as they battle for a place in the grand finale in a wedding themed roast. Comedian Katherine Ryan guest judges.
